Board of DirectorsManagement




OUR DIRECTORSSally Beauty Holding's Board of Directors is responsible for fiduciary oversight, setting policies for the corporation, and acting in the best interests of the corporation and its stockholders. Our Board is comprised of 10 directors whose leadership and diverse knowledge bring a wealth of experience to our company.
View our Board of Directors
OUR EXECUTIVE TEAMThe Sally Beauty Holding's Executive Leadership team averages 24 years of beauty industry experience and possesses a unique combination of proven leadership and deep industry knowledge.
